window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A unique spin on Fae, Angels, Werewolves, Demons, Vampires, and soulmates.</b></p> <p><i>All these young lovers want is a happily ever after. In every life they’ve lived, they haven’t made it to the happy ending they crave so badly. Will they get it right this time?</i></p> <p>Laila Callidy and Jeremy Skoulda are a pair of legendary soulmates - known as the par animarum - that even the supernatural world has always believed to be a myth. A fairytale whispered from generation to generation, told only by word of mouth.<br> <br> The old story varies, but some aspects always remain the same.<br> One: The pairs are cursed by a jealous god that feared their strength.<br> Two: Their love for one another is strong enough to create and destroy worlds.<br> Three: Once every pair has found their match, a war unlike any ever seen will commence.<br> <br> Laila and Jeremy though? They don’t want a war. All they want is one another. A simple, human life where they can forget about chasing rogue Demons and Vampires.<br> <br> But they never get what they strive for without a battle.<br> <i>If you like the darkness and gore of Laurell K. Hamilton, the wit of Kim Harrison, the character development of Karen Marie Moning, and the suspense of Kelley Armstrong, then the Eluding Destiny series is for you.</i></p> <p>(Updated format and manuscript)<br> Recommended listening order:<br> <i>Eluding Destiny Prequel - Blood Bar<br> Eluding Destiny Book I<br> Eluding Destiny Book II - New Normal: Celena's Story Part I<br> Eluding Destiny Book III - The Horrors that Created Us<br> Eluding Destiny Book IV - Aftershocks<br> Eluding Destiny Book V - Reprisal</i><br> And many more to come</p>"; 
